FROM ubuntu:14.04

ENV LC_ALL C
ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND noninteractive

    apt-get -y --no-install-recommends install git curl build-essential && \

USER nobody
ENV HOME /skarnet-builder
WORKDIR /skarnet-builder

CMD ["/skarnet-builder/build-wrapper"]
